    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) reflects the inherent limitation of ASTM F1717 single-configuration protocol and is accepted given direct regulatory standard compliance and corroborating clinical evidence. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all primary QoIs across N=11 specimens at two independent laboratories. Overall credibility assessment: ACCEPTED for the stated COU.",
